=== shoulder surfing ===
Gather details by looking over someone's shoulder

--- Locations/examples ---
* Airports/flights
* Hallway facing monitors
* Coffee shops
* Using Binoculars/telescopes
* Webcam monitoring

--- Protect against shoulder surfing ---
* Control your input, be aware of surroundings
* Use privacy filters
* Keep your monitor out of sight (hallways and windows)
* Don't sit in front of someone suspicious
